commit.message: Add C-w shortcut to close application windows
Change "as root" to a comment

Compile gschema files after installing

As per http://mesonbuild.com/Porting-from-autotools.html#gsettings ,
we need to compile the gsettings schema by hand after installing the
file.

Fixes #30.

Merge pull request #28 from rilian-la-te/master

Meson port and other improvements
Add Russian translation

Change build system to meson

As the GTK world is moving to Meson, it makes sense to move this
project as well.

Merge pull request #21 from Generator/master

Update Portuguese translation
Merge remote-tracking branch 'upstream/master'
Update Portuguese translation
Version bump to 1.1.1
doc: Add openconnect to README.md as dependency

doc: Update docs about launch options

Add the --no-icon to the man page, and add all launch options
to README.md.

Closes #18.

main: Add option to disable status icon

This makes it easier to get out of a situation with a broken
tray and launch-to-tray enabled.

At the same time, refactor option handling a bit, so that main.c
doesn't have to deal with defaults coming from config, and can just
act on values like status_icon_enabled etc.

status: Set technologies without services inactive

This beautifies the menu for technologies without services.

Closes #17.

main: Only launch to tray if status icon is enabled

Previously, status icon could be disabled but the program
still could be launched to tray, rendering users helpless.

Fixes #15.
Version bump to 1.1
README: Change GTK dependency from 3.14 to 3.10
po: Update Finnish translation
build: Fix distcheck errors
status: Fix warnings if status icon not enabled

config: Fix compilation warning

Compiling without available config options warns about
unused variables. Also fix the .c file defining the
header guard.

main: Improve parameter handling

Appropriately hide parameters if support is not compiled in. If
user tries to use a parameter without support compiled in, log
a warning.

main: Fix compilation failure

Running ./configure --disable-status-icon fails compilation because
of missing macros.

doc: Add a simple man page

Closes #11.

m4: Add missing dependecy

Without ax_require_defined, the build fails for systems
without GNU's autoconf-archive.

status: Update status icon on state changes

When a service state changes, update status icon to the best
available status icon.

Closes #9.

main: Add config option for launching to tray

In addition, add also a command line option for tray launching. These
can be used for users who want autolaunched gtk applet without having
to separately close the window.

settings: Fix some properties not being sent

Some properties were not correctly detected that they should
be sent to connmand. Also remove empty strings from lists
before sending them.
